These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
4 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the chinese is on the left or right of the german##3
4. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
5. the mexican is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
6. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
7. the chinese is somewhere between the brazilian and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
8. the chinese and the owner of the rat have the same parity positions##9
9. the german and the owner of the ferret have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | chinese | german     | mexican |
| Pet           | hamster   | rat     | guinea-pig | ferret  |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, cola, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, sudoku, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is traveling and the person drinking coffee have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
8. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea     | cola    | almond-milk | coffee    |
| Hobby      | dancing | drawing | sudoku      | traveling |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta, milk
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, mango, pumpkin
1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
8. the person drinking cola and the person eating avocado have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | cola    | fanta   | coffee    | milk  |
| Food       | avocado | pumpkin | artichoke | mango |

