.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, security-guard, software-developer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, reggae, trance
1. the fan hip-hop is the dressmaker##1
2. the fan indie is on the right of the fan reggae##1
3. the fan indie is somewhere to the left of the dressmaker##5
4. the fan trance is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
5. the fan indie is on the left of the coach##1
6. the software-developer and the fan trance have the same parity positions##9
7. the security-guard is on the left or right of the coach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | software-developer | security-guard | coach  | dressmaker |
| Music-Genre   | reggae             | indie          | trance | hip-hop    |

