.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, punk, salsa
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, sailing, skateboarding, soccer
1. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
2. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
3. the person who's sport is soccer and the fan salsa have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the fan salsa is not to the right of the fan punk##8
6. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan punk##5
7. the fan salsa is somewhere to the right of the fan funk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | hip-hop | salsa         | punk     |
| Sport         | sailing | soccer  | skateboarding | lacrosse |

