The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, puzzles, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person eating strawberry##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person eating lettuce have different parity positions##9
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food    | strawberry | asparagus | grapefruit   | lettuce   |
| Hobby   | skydiving  | puzzles   | magic-tricks | gardening |

