.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, lemon, nectarine, peach
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, italian, turkish
1. the person eating peach is not the turkish##6
2. the turkish is not to the right of the canadian##8
3. the person eating nectarine is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
4. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
5. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the italian##3
6. the turkish is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
8. the person eating garlic is the colombian##1
9. the person eating peach and the canadian have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | lemon   | peach    | nectarine | garlic    |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian | italian   | colombian |

