1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is skydiving have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk    | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | soy-milk |
| Hobby      | puzzles | skydiving   | board-games   | baking   |

